                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For related documentation, see <ref target="frus1943v01">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1943, vol. I</ref>, index entries
                    under “Refugees From Europe and the Middle East, governmental efforts for relief
                    of”, and especially (for the immediate background of the discussions of the
                        <gloss target="#t_Trident1">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Trident</hi>
                    </gloss> Conference) Hull’s memorandum of May 7, 1943, and Roosevelt’s reply of
                    May 14, <ref target="frus1943v01#pg_176">
                        <hi rend="italic">ibid.</hi>, pp. 176</ref>–<ref target="frus1943v01#pg_179"
                        >179</ref>.</p>
            </div>
